onunciation, and partly from association with Germanic-origin names such as   Ronald .  This name is strongly associated with clan Macdonald, the clan of the medieval Lords of the Isles, but is now also widely used by families with no Scottish connections."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Donald Kirkpatrick was born in 1110, in Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He married Kirkpatrick about 1136, in Scotland, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1110–":"1110–Surnud","1110–Female":"1110–Surnud","1128–1150":"1128–1150","1110–Male":"1110–Surnud","1128":"1128","1110":"1110","Abt 1128":"umbes 1128","about 1136":"umbes 1136","1150":"1150","Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1110–":"1110–Kuollut","1110–Female":"1110–Kuollut","1128–1150":"1128–1150","1110–Male":"1110–Kuollut","1128":"1128","1110":"1110","Abt 1128":"noin 1128","about 1136":"noin 1136","1150":"1150","Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Scotland":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1110–":"1110–Décédé","1110–Female":"1110–Décédée","1128–1150":"1128–1150","1110–Male":"1110–Décédé","1128":"1128","1110":"1110","Abt 1128":"environ 1128","about 1136":"environ 1136","1150":"1150","Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Scotland":"Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Donald Kirkpatrick est né en 1110, à Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Kirkpatrick environ 1136, à Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1110–":"1110–Verstorben","1110–Female":"1110–Verstorben","1128–1150":"1128–1150","1110–Male":"1110–Verstorben","1128":"1128","1110":"1110","Abt 1128":"um 1128","about 1136":"um 1136","1150":"1150","Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Closeburn, Dumfriesshire, Schottland, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Schottland, Unite